====[http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1537511003000187 Temperature gradients in a partially shaded large greenhouse equipped with evaporative cooling pads]<ref>Kittas, C., Bartzanas, T., & Jaffrin, A. (2003).  Biosystems Engineering, 85(1), 87-94.</ref>====

