====[http://link.springer.com/article/10.1007%2Fs004420050968 Stomatal behavior and photosynthetic performance under dynamic light regimes in a seasonally dry tropical rain forest]<ref>Allen, M. T., & Pearcy, R. W. (2000).  Oecologia, 122(4), 470-478.</ref>====

