====[http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0927024806003345  Efficiency model for photovoltaic modules and demonstration of its application to energy yield estimation]<ref>Durisch, W., Bitnar, B., Mayor, J. C., Kiess, H., Lam, K. H., & Close, J. (2007). Solar energy materials and solar cells, 91(1), 79-84.</ref>====

