====[http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.1530-9290.2011.00439.x/full Life cycle greenhouse gas emissions of crystalline silicon photovoltaic electricity generation]<ref>Hsu, D. D., O’Donoughue, P., Fthenakis, V., Heath, G. A., Kim, H. C., Sawyer, P., ... & Turney, D. E. (2012). . Journal of Industrial Ecology, 16(s1), S122-S135.</ref>====

'''Abstract:'''
