====[http://ieeexplore.ieee.org/xpls/abs_all.jsp?arnumber=7355759&tag=1 More solar farms or more bioenergy crops? Mapping and assessing potential land-use conflicts among renewable energy technologies in eastern Ontario, Canada.]<ref>K. Calvert, W. Mabee (2015). Applied Geography, Volume 56, January 2015, Pages 209-221, ISSN 0143-6228 </ref>====

