====[http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1876610214013800 Performance Reduction of PV Systems by Dust Deposition.]<ref>Bernd Weber, Angélica Quiñones, Rafael Almanza, M. Dolores Duran (2014). Energy Procedia, Volume 57, 2014, Pages 99-108, ISSN 1876-6102, http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.egypro.2014.10.013 </ref>====

