====[http://www.scientific.net/AMM.737.20 Influence of Solar Panels in Distributed Photovoltaic Power Generating System above Farm Land on Field and Crops.]<ref>Ge Z., Xiao R., Wang R.(2015). Applied Mechanics and Materials, Vol. 737, pp. 20-23, Mar. 2015</ref>====

