====[http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1364032115011740 Advanced applications of solar energy in agricultural greenhouses.]<ref>Hassanien R., Li M., Lin W. (2015) Renewable and Sustainable Energy Reviews, Volume 54, February 2016, Pages 989-1001, ISSN 1364-0321, http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.rser.2015.10.095.</ref>====

